Package: aRxiv
Title: Programmatic interface to full-text search for arXiv
Version: 0.4
Date: 2014-09-16
Authors@R: c(person("Karthik", "Ram", role="aut",
    email="karthik.ram@gmail.com"),
    person("Karl", "Broman", rol=c("aut","cre"),
    email="kbroman@biostat.wisc.edu"))
Description: A programmatic interface to the API for arXiv, an
    electronic archive and distribution server for research articles
    (covered areas include physics, mathematics, computer science,
    quantitative biology, quantitative finance, and statistics).
URL: https://github.com/ropensci/aRxiv
BugReports: https://github.com/ropensci/aRxiv/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
    httr,
    XML
Suggests:
    devtools,
    roxygen2,
    testthat,
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
LazyData: true
